    Class and Description
    EventsExchangingI
    The interface EventsExchangingI declares the method used to propagate events among models and simulation engines in a DEVS simulation.
    ModelDescriptionI
    The interface ModelDescriptionI declares the methods that can be used to get information from simulation models directly or through their simulation engine or any other proxy reference.
    VariablesSharingI
    The interface VariablesSharingI defines methods related to the sharing of variables among HIOA models.
